Cobble - Hostage Rescue
by DaveJ (http://www.johnsto.co.uk/)
Textures by Valve
CS-Remix by CoCoNUT/ http://coconut.de.tc

Counter-Terrorists:

Rescue the hostages
or eliminate those nasty terrorists.
"Go forth and kick ass, soldiers."

Terrorists:

"You failed again to plant the bomb?
So these people belong to Lord Williams 
staff. Make sure nobody can rescue them."
"SIR, YES SIR!"

There are 4 hostages and 2 rescue zones.
